snippet: A deal was said to have been reached on cuts of about $9 billion over 10 years to the food stamp program, but disagreements continued over dairy and catfish programs.
abstract: Deal is said to be reached in new farm bill on cuts of about $9 billion over 10 years to the food stamp program, but disagreements continue over dairy and catfish programs.
